---item_651 Tanky Pulse---
Type :: Equippable
Slot :: Active 
Icon :: items_727
Gun Definition :: [[Tanky Pulse]]
Rarity :: Legendary
Durability :: 4

On use, reduces damage from enemy attacks for 2 seconds. If the player has Taunt echo nodes unlocked enemies will be aggroed and damage reduction duration will increase. 

The earth vitalizes you and if you've got the juice it will draw enemies towards you. 

